title: Ubehage's Picture Finder
description:
Ubehage's Picture Finder
------------------------

This is a small, simple and easy application that will scan any folder(s) you select and find all files containing a picture.

Imagine this scenario:
Somebody renamed all your files, and you no longer have any idea what is what.
With this application, you can at least find all your pictures :)

Screenshot: 
http://i.imgur.com/k0aZ4Mr.jpg


/Ubehage
